snippet.title: Introduction to Open Tournament: Development Log 1
snippet.description:
Open Tournament is a futuristic first person shooter where players master innovative weapons and dynamic movement to prove they are the best. Open Tournament is an open-source project currently in development by a community of veteran developers & Unreal Tournament fans.

For more information about Open Tournament game, or information on how to join our development team visit our website: https://www.opentournamentgame.com

Discord: https://discord.gg/Rw8evNT
Twitch: https://www.twitch.tv/OpenTournament

This development log focuses on introducing Open Tournament and discussing progress for the first year of development. As Open Tournament is an open-sourced project, developers are also encouraged to get involved and help improve Open Tournament as we head into the next stages of development.

#OT #OpenTournament #UnrealEngine
